  "3112170": {
    "name": "Dice Legends",
    "steam_appid": 3112170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/e3a918f67b3b633be83a5500db54ef79.avif?t=1768307456\" width=1200 height=522 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《骰子传奇》是一款由独立团队开发的单人肉鸽游戏，其成员曾参与<i>《巫师之昆特牌》</i>和<i>《赛博朋克：边缘行者》</i>的创意设计。<br><br>此外，团队还邀请到<i>《小丑牌》（</i>Balatro<i>）</i>的作曲家操刀原创配乐。在游戏的深度奇幻世界中，你可以选择使用不同骰子（6面骰/8面骰/12面骰）的角色展开冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/0ffce451b8492162f1f77a0c58f6a094.poster.avif?t=1768307456\" width=798 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/0ffce451b8492162f1f77a0c58f6a094.webm?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/0ffce451b8492162f1f77a0c58f6a094.mp4?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每击败一个怪物，就能获得增强构筑战术的新卡牌。但组牌只是游戏乐趣的一小部分—还需要利用道具、卡牌组合与强化效果来驾驭骰子的随机性。游戏的精髓在于运用理解、策略配合未知的运气，创造令人大呼过瘾的破局组合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1f91d38b817dbe9cd58996776b8b253.poster.avif?t=1768307456\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1f91d38b817dbe9cd58996776b8b253.webm?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1f91d38b817dbe9cd58996776b8b253.mp4?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/19da1729aed04b1c23138e352e374e53.avif?t=1768307456\" width=1200 height=522 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每回合将投掷一组骰子，并从牌堆中抽取卡牌。接着，运用骰子激活卡牌：构筑防御体系，对敌施加负面状态，或是输出全部伤害。发掘越多的卡牌+骰子组成的协同效应，你的连招就将愈发势不可挡—同时也更具畅快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/faffd75be84a3781bbd0b1f062da3982.avif?t=1768307456\" width=1200 height=522 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从三位精通不同骰子的英雄中做出你的选择：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雄狮圣骑士ARIE—精通6面骰子，既能爆发毁灭性伤害，又能构筑护盾抵御来袭攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸦人召唤师KURO—精通12面骰子，能召唤并驱使强大的魔物协助作战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >树蛙刺客XIN—敏捷的暗影术士，精通8面骰子，既能持续积攒伤害，亦可发动致命暴击。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1b8231d41debf3e10e5733c1e42f467.poster.avif?t=1768307456\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1b8231d41debf3e10e5733c1e42f467.webm?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/d1b8231d41debf3e10e5733c1e42f467.mp4?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/bb0bd17dc48902a02ad3f6042ee47597.avif?t=1768307456\" width=1200 height=522 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将进入遭遇灾变的怪异世界，在那里，所有人类都因某种神秘的魔法变成了骇人的怪物。在穿越地图寻找线索、揭开故事真相的旅途中，去往何方与探索何处完全由你决定。每次成功清理一个地点，你都将获得能塑造战斗体系的武器、护甲、饰品等丰厚奖励。一旦打造出终极装备与卡牌组合，你就可以击败最终首领，成为真正的骰子传奇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/089246aabc1e95ce7bb4c142e1cfac16.poster.avif?t=1768307456\" width=682 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/089246aabc1e95ce7bb4c142e1cfac16.webm?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112170/extras/089246aabc1e95ce7bb4c142e1cfac16.mp4?t=1768307456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >160张手绘卡牌，提供多样协同与连击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+拥有多重技能的敌人考验你的最强卡组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个视觉风格迥异的世界—每个世界都有专属怪物与挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3位英雄，拥有各自的独特风格与完全不同的构筑机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75+可供角色装备或战斗中使用的道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界观和剧情由<i>《巫师之昆特牌》</i>及<i>《赛博朋克：边缘行者》</i>的制作人与<i>《巫师：浪人》</i>与<i>《</i>No\\Name<i>》</i>漫画编剧— Rafał Jaki 构思创作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏原声配乐由《小丑牌》（Balatro）作曲家LouisF操刀制作</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 简体中文, 乌克兰语",
